{"tid":1234272,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民意同勇武其實可以並存","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T01:57:06.000Z","uid":10281,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5837c43b8a29b035aecd3ff408d5580ff31d4098","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:25.000Z","msg":"琴日嗌得最多嘅除咗針對撒回條例之外，就一定係針對林鄭。<br />\n勇武要衝唔緊要，唔好死衝爛衝，我地唔為啖氣，暫時唔為報仇住，不過學下跟隨民意啦。<br />\n<br />\n既然立會冇咩用，仲要敗緊家，不如⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df83b00f4111bd8064cb37df745f725dab9e6c37","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d8494b61c94bd798308bec95367773765badc6","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5877afb4b503a3fc3c999e87b13ea2af53aa566","tid":1234272,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"依家最怕就係政府冷處理，咁我地個勢點可以去到七一"},{"pid":"808cd7559bc11ddb14d746797098a1ca373e6c67","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔係搞分化，打一場仗係講緊回樣分配資源。<br />\n人嘅動員力有限，心力有限，財力有限，民氣更有限。點解要浪費係冇咩用嘅位置？<br />\n要玩就玩得聰明啲，唔好俾嗰少少嘅馬路限制自己，香港咁大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c62f46686df20cbf39d38e949b299505f612ae","tid":1234272,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51f50086d212a71889d9feae33f13b0958ebe8ff","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"玩裝備又唔夠警察玩喇，而且衝完冇咩用，仲要倒輸埋個勢。<br />\n香港人最貪新鮮，玩社運都要新鮮，當然暫時唔亂衝立法會同政總喇，但我地可以去第二度架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港咁大</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌你老未暗示晒唔該用下個死人腦</span>"},{"pid":"123e967ef07ccf2061ab717c5ff9853c0878567c","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"我從來都唔撚會篤灰，不過會諗下點樣先可以運用本身有嘅優勢。<br />\n呢一刻分散投資真係麻麻地，兄弟爬山唔係一個好嘅戰術，我地太容易被分化。<br />\n<br />\n但呢幾年嘅分化係邊個帶我地和解？係林鄭呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5195edc2356e3fee6ee7cc48b480008bab8e22d7","tid":1234272,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb106652309952c270008afb7a84e36bea820452","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"所以大家千祈唔好失焦，你搞鳩條馬路有咩為，又唔係條馬路送你中。<br />\n有力嘅不如做下實事，條馬路無辜架喎，聽下大眾主流意見，走咪走。<br />\n走去邊就大家話事喇，出面都有幾個post講緊有個好地方喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138a1cf244757af64baed6c91153603855e7702","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8705de8ef6a98994bcc8e2460c96f06267675b3c","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5195edc2356e3fee6ee7cc48b480008bab8e22d7","tid":1234272,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:13.000Z","msg":"拿巴打，千祈唔好亂講野，我好和平理性非暴力。<br />\n雖然我唔篤灰，但我鼓勵大家絕～～～對唔好亂黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4e0540131b8d9b3d2da65f66f02acd5affe21b","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"如果大家認同請幫推，同埋幫手提下勇武嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用連動同健身都要用正確嘅力喇，打仗又點可以亂咁打呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dac7ad9146aba9699ca0296733f4ebdb59023ca","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b2c883b6b9305de4079a1c1188ee03e7bb4c25a","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:41:09.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得共產黨點樣打遊擊，係靠攻其不備呀。屌你老未次撚次都玩同一個地方，你唔悶班警賊都悶喇，不如大家搞下新意思。"},{"pid":"c937d70641959b5b8c72d646eb449a9e97bab162","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"而家班警察以逸待勞，又扮撚晒溫和，之後放針係政總外同網路上分化大家，乜你地甘心咩。<br />\n要團結大家，就要知道乜野位最trigger到民眾。"},{"pid":"ba8036d76c76770f06ac93a5fd03b685e4c57b1b","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:45:48.000Z","msg":"打一場仗個焦點好重要，唔好又反送中又反人工島又反乜反物咁多口號住，我地對抗呢一個攻權好明顯乜撚都要反。<br />\n<br />\n所以，焦點係政權嘅代表度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c72af6503744ccc21af417e66e014060f97cf51","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d7dccc3d92f49052e0834f6ba150bcc557f3d59","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ded222af98c8f084d276288c4aa0d256473bbaa1","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5877afb4b503a3fc3c999e87b13ea2af53aa566","tid":1234272,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"依家最怕就係政府冷處理，咁我地個勢點可以去到七一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"咁咪逼鳩佢熱處理囉，做一啲野可以令佢地冇得扮唔知架啵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9140425925b4532325473b36a059b5c529cbc081","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"請大家聽從民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa140ac95d4cdc38568a8a35f1b1b54ceafcbe73","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d68145ceae5c887cbeab93771521a9c135bfd399","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"41f256cc8888f3978a1059984eb6961e78709467","tid":1234272,"uid":10281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}